{"tid":1512742,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［大方向］願景：港獨  目標：五大訴求  實際行動：迫出老解/緊急法","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:09:36.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"170d32032ee66e568bce7ee59ad7beccc27a47b1","tid":1512742,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"開天殺價，落地還錢<br />\n<br />\n抗爭既實際操作要迫佢緊急法，甚至派軍落黎。<br />\n<br />\n如果佢係唔會出，只要迫到佢埋牆角佢無路退就會開始答應訴求。無論結局係點，共產黨都係輸，分別在於佢輸多定輸少。<br />\n<br />\n而往後既抗爭就算你是否支持港獨也好也必須圍繞住港獨，所以無論如何整個民運一定要有獨立既聲音。如果今日大家仲係咁抗拒香港唔係中國一部分既聲音既話，好有可能會為將來失敗埋下種子！<br />\n<br />\n十年前和平遊行俾共產黨屌<br />\n今日和平遊行俾共産黨讚<br />\n<br />\n自己諗"},{"pid":"a4264fbd43301c99e60e86e2ea609e73f645b513","tid":1512742,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=3df52eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=54f57b1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=a3f596df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"585f6332a10b95b43d0218a68ca5f974ef59c920","tid":1512742,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 停止國泰白色恐怖 愛丁堡廣場</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">今晚見</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港 時代革命</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span>"},{"pid":"9ec716a5a66572d3beeffe1eb843182832118243","tid":1512742,"uid":172443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJLGv0x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJLGv0x.gif&h=e32fe2f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff2653c2d2847a24e26c2113a5685c5530f12cc9","tid":1512742,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"〔過牆梯〕淆底唔敢入機場既同我入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512735</a>"},{"pid":"d43d89dff7f6c99ad11a88cb960b911786145f62","tid":1512742,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"無錯 五大訴求係手段 唔係目的<br />\n佢接受咗而家五大訴求 而你地唔再出嚟<br />\n咁香港人就真係輸咗<br />\n所以係要 set到佢無可能接受"},{"pid":"d9ce362c062ecee49b3b91b771a273c3445313a6","tid":1512742,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"而家就係因為冇條件 佢先可以咁強硬<br />\n百萬人 唔施壓嘅話 只不過係一個數字<br />\n<br />\n點先有條件？<br />\n只要你可以癱瘓香港/重挫經濟<br />\n然後佢又冇有效方法可以停止到<br />\n就會迫住佢出返嚟 主導權去返我地度<br />\n<br />\n所以唔係完全係諗點同警察對抗<br />\n係要諗點先可以攬炒<br />\n以攬炒為手段 迫使政府讓步<br />\n<br />\n未必要同警察直接衝突<br />\n只要你話畀佢知一個訊息 你唔跪低嘅<br />\n我地可以玩得更加盡就得<br />\n有人話佔領商場 減低消費意欲<br />\n都可以係一種方法<br />\n甚至乎一啲更加激進嘅<br />\n只係你敢唔敢去諗 同埋做<br />\n個個都話攬炒 你地有幾多個真係想攬炒"}]}